WWW::Adblock
============

This module is a very simple Perl implementation of the Adblock Plus 
extension for Firefox.  Currently it supports URL filtering but not
element blocking.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

   perl Makefile.PL
   make
   make test
   make install

